name: Bunga Laut Bungalow
address: Jl. Setra, Purwakerti, Kec. Abang, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80852, Indonesia
review 1:
We booked a 2-storey bungalow for 3 people, 1 double bed upstairs with a balcony and one single bed downstairs. They allowed our dog to stay the night too, thank you for that. There is however only 1 air condition in the room, installed upstairs, so the room downstairs was hot even after we maxed the AC.

The area is nice and very quiet since it is quite far from the main road. The swimming pool is really nice. For divers, there is a dive shop next door.

The staff who checked us in was friendly, but the one who was on duty the next day until we checked out was not so. Also when we asked to make our breakfast and keep them until we came back from a snorkeling trip, they said okay, but when we wanted to claim it, they said they didn't make it. But the hotel manager Pak Made was kind, he granted our request for late check out due to our snorkeling trip, thank you Pak Made.
review 2: Very nice hotel.  Deluxe rooms, specially the shower! Very good food and nice staff.  Easy to book diving activity with excellemt monitors.
review 3: Friendly staff, nice bungalow that is out of the main street, the provided food and menu are not that great.. But there are a lot of great warung (small restaurant) within 30minutes drive
review 4: This is best place for indian food in Bali, Wonderful atmosphere and lovely staff
review 5: Amazing place close with amed beach
